  "text": "To close the gap between theory and practice, thorough theoretical analysis is required. We believe that theoretical understanding of learning from weakly supervised data could potentially provide guidelines on how to design and train effective models using weak supervision. In this position paper, we review our recent theoretical findings that shed light on learning from weakly supervised data for information retrieval. Refer to [CITATION_1] for more details.",
